---
title: Roasted Veggie Farro Bowls with Marinated Cranberries & Salsa Verde Sunflower Pepitas
description: Farro, a variety of hulled wheat, is praised for its chewy texture and nutty flavor. To make this bowl shine, we pair the tasty ancient grain with roasted sweet potatoes and onion, peppery arugula, sweet-tart marinated cranberries, lemony dressing, nutty Parmesan cheese, and our own Salsa Verde Sunflower Pepitas. Get ready to be bowled over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60eef03b2b8e1d36473eb0f6-66611c57.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/roasted-veggie-farro-bowls-60eef03b2b8e1d36473eb0f6-30a08c9d.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/roasted-veggie-farro-bowls-60eef03b2b8e1d36473eb0f6
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
cuisine: North America
time required: 40 minutes
